{"tid":435636,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲天才通常都有超於常人嘅記憶力？","createTime":"2017-10-14T12:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T21:43:18.000Z","uid":148531,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8341bc58c1b54088aa12290c41a72f6373baab3f","tid":435636,"uid":148531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:45:57.000Z","msg":"但係點解記憶力好就可以係考試（不限於香港）贏曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢啲記憶力差嘅人 就預咗做弱智 預定要食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回看歷史 我都發覺 偉人 通常都係記憶力勁好嘅人<br />\n<br />\n睇啲數學天才 大學教授 全部都係記憶力超勁 講嘢都好快接唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好勁<br />\n雖然我否認有IQ呢樣嘢存在 但總係有啲人有天生advantage<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f35f1da2f589c497589c65ad74a2a395df5c30","tid":435636,"uid":137741,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:46:29.000Z","msg":"記憶力好所以係天才<br />\n定係<br />\n天才所以記憶力好"},{"pid":"0aa0b574dc2a112583642dd6fa5993111ba7638e","tid":435636,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"記憶力好嘅人<br />\n係記憶力天才"},{"pid":"4be49954be07645995454975b70bdc98ef5370f0","tid":435636,"uid":22826,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:47:54.000Z","msg":"樓主 天生我才必有用<br />\n我覺得我地人生有趣味d<br />\n叻左係做廢青到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cefa2b70a9729d3577267c0855e6179b4215a9","tid":435636,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:48:05.000Z","msg":"有類人只係記某D野特別好"},{"pid":"2aef583c2c3295f54686f69e1c850fce508f0452","tid":435636,"uid":148531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:52:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記憶力好所以係天才<br />\n定係<br />\n天才所以記憶力好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩者都係 mutual relationship"},{"pid":"f45c57bd8ccf958c273b2294a3c450243541a267","tid":435636,"uid":56015,"like":